  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The goal of this study was to test the safety and efficacy of this stapler in our general&#xD;
      thoracic surgery practice.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      A prospective study was conducted with 80 consecutive thoracic cases. Stapler usage data,&#xD;
      intraoperative outcomes, and 30-day post-operative outcomes were evaluated.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
